title: BUG: Underworld poro ward skin shows up as Dragonslayer poro ward skin when used as a vision ward
body: Title as above - I don't own this particular ward skin (It's not even available for purchase yet!) and I've double and triple checked :) Is this a known bug?

replies.body:
31/9/12

lol

But yeah, report it to [this board](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report). I actually had a friend who was telling me about this a while back.
